components.text:
Test your game. How many points can you score? If your game is too easy, you can:

	+ Give the player less time;
	+ Have more balloons;
	+ Make the balloons move faster;
	+ Make the balloons smaller.

	Test your game a few times until you're happy that it's the right level of difficulty.

In your game, you'll use a different number to represent each colour:

	+ 1 = red;
	+ 2 = blue;
	+ 3 = green;
	+ 4 = yellow.

	Give your character 4 different colour costumes, one for each of the 4 colours above. Make sure that your coloured costumes are in the right order.
